-l10 = Large column width 10X5%=50%

-t20 = Tab column width 20X5%=100%

-m20 = Mobile column width 20X5%=100%

-s15 = Small column width 15X5%=75%

-to = For Contents Slide Up & Down

-sh = For Contents Show & Hide

-cn = For Content Display None

-.cd = On Hover To Display Content

-sp7 = Side Sup Content Seven & Side Sup Main Content Seven Gets Activated

-ma15 = Side Macro Content Fifteen & Side Macro Main Content Fifteen Gets Activated

-mi31 = Side Micro Content Thirty One & Side Micro Main Content Thirty One Gets Activated

For Page Actions

-pa1: = For Page actions & 1 Act As Index

-to = For Toggle Actions

-sh = For Show & Hide Actions

-ih = For Individual Show & Hide Actions

-ec1(2) = For Element Click One Of Page Index & Two Of Element Index

-ea1(2) = For Element Action One Of Page Index & Two Of Element Index

-su-ec1(3) = For Sub Element Click One Of Page Index & Three Of Element Index

-su-ea2(3) = For Sub Element Click One Of Page Index & Three Of Element Index

-sp-ec1(4) = For Super Element Click One Of Page Index & Four Of Element Index

-sp-ea1(4) = For Super Element Click One Of Page Index & Four Of Element Index

-ma-ec1(5) = For Macro Element Click One Of Page Index & Five Of Element Index

-ma-ea1(5) = For Macro Element Click One Of Page Index & Five Of Element Index

-mi-ec1(1) = For Micro Element Click One Of Page Index & One Of Element Index

-mi-ea1(1)= For Micro Element Click One Of Page Index & One Of Element Index

-a1 = For Element Action One In Active State

-su2 = For Sub Element Action Two In Active State

-sp3 = For Super Element Action Three In Active State

-ma4 = For Macro Element Action Four In Active State

-mi5 = For Micro Element Action Five In Active State

-cn = For ea Display None

-.cd = On Hover To Display Content

For Graphs

cell-gr

-gv1:= For Vertical Graph Actions

-gh1:= For Horizontal Graph Actions

-g10(20)= For Graph X-axis 10 points && Y-axis 20-points

-wh25(25)= Width 25px And Height 25px Of Graph Bar Cell

-fc4= Bar Full Background Color Four

-fs14(12)= X-axis Points Font-Size 14px and Y-Axis Points Font-Size 12px

-ab= For X-axis and Y-Axis Borders

For Vertical Span Cells

-x1: = For X-Axis Index

-ba2(10) = Bar starts @ Y-2 Ends @ Y-10

-bc1 = For Individual Bar Background Color One

-cc1(5) = For Highlighting Bar Cell With Background Color Five

For Horizontal Span Cells

-y1: = For Y-Axis Index

-ba2(10) = Bar starts @ X-2 Ends @ X-10

-bc1 = For Individual Bar Background Color One

-cc1(5) = For Highlighting Bar Cell With Background Color Five

For Page To page Content Transfer(Ajax-Layout)

cell-pc

-pc1(1):-se = Page One & Sends Content One To -pc1(1):-re

For Combo

cell-cm

Column Has c1 To c20 Sizes

-c10 = column width 10X5%=50%

-d4 = Desktop column width 4X5%=20%

-l10 = Large column width 10X5%=50%

-t20 = Tab column width 20X5%=100%

-m20 = Mobile column width 20X5%=100%

-s15 = Small column width 15X5%=75%

-cl = Individual column Align Left

-cc = Individual column Align Center

-cr= Individual column Align Right

-cs= Column Streched

-wi25= Width 25px

-wi.25= Width 25%

-ht25= Height 25px

-pa25= Padding 25px

-ma25= Margin 25px

-ra25= Border-Radius 25px

-ra.25= Border-Radius 25%

-bg2= background Color Two

-bo15(2)= border Size 15px Color Two

-w15(2)= Shadow To Top Left Corner 15px Wide With Color Two

-x15(2)= Shadow To Top Right Corner 15px Wide With Color Two

-y15(2)= Shadow To Bottom Left Corner 15px Wide With Color Two

-z15(2)= Shadow To Bottom Right Corner 15px Wide With Color Two
